<p>Users trust organic results more than ads. The data proves it.</p>
<p>According to <a href="https://backlinko.com/google-ctr-stats">Backlinko's CTR study</a>, the #1 organic result gets a 27.6% click-through rate. The average Google Search ad gets 3 to 5%.</p>
